  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nWhen you change the cursor position by mouse to the beginning of the mention and try to insert any letter - it will be added at the end of the mention (plus mention will be selected)\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nInput mention, move the cursor by mouse click to the beginning of the mention, try to add any letter\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/117639195/207059853-19a09c43-a8c6-4718-b0ed-69763d3c55a6.mov\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nthe letter is added before the mention\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nthe letter is added after the mention and the mention is selecting\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: 0.8.0\r\n- Operating System: macos\r\n\r\n",
